<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA30">
<l>piṟaraṟiya lākāp perumaiyarun tāmē</l>
<l>piṟaraṟiyum pēruṇarvun tāmē - piṟaruṭaiya</l>
<l>veṉpē yaṇintiravi ṟīyāṭu memmāṉār</l>
<l>vaṉpēyun tāmu makiḻntu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without being known to others he is of greatness</l>
<l>and he is great perception known to others. Adorning himself</l>
<l>with other people’s bones at night our father dance with fire,</l>
<l>the strong demonesses and himself being delighted.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
